reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good price , the case I've been looking for !
reviews.reviewText: I love that it doesn't have a front screen protector because those usually effect the touch sensitivity. So far a good sturdy case, side buttons easy to use and it's comfy to hold, doesn't slip out of your hands. I drop my phone all the time and needed a drop proof case this is it! Great price too and love the color . Just make sure you put it on right, it comes apart in 3 or 4 pieces don't try to it on as one piece like me 😑

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great cell phone case, after you figure out how to get it on.
reviews.reviewText: I love everything about this phone cover, EXCEPT that there were no instructions as to how to put it on. Thank goodness that a previous buyer had left a review saying that it has to be taken apart to get it on. It DOES come apart in 3 pieces. The pastel color has to be popped out of the dark color. The pastel color is hard and fits on the phone. The dark color is more flexible and stretches over the phone and hard case. It fits my phone perfectly! All the ports and buttons match up exactly right. Love the colors and the feel of the case!

reviews.reviewText: This is a great product. Fits my phone like a glove. Case is 2 parts and locks the phone in between the layers. This does not include a screen protector but the case protrudes maybe an 1/8th inch from the glass so I think it offers good protection for the screen. The case also has a flap that you need to hold back in order to put the charger in place. Takes a little getting used to but keeps the charging port clean.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 9, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice case, but not for me
reviews.reviewText: No instructions on how to put it on correctly, so it was quite a struggle. However once it was on, it felt like a sturdy, durable case.The reason I don't like it... The phone itself is quite large, and this case adds quite a bit more bulk and weight. Not an issue for some, but I have smallish hands and the hand holding the phone literally started to ache after just a short time. So I'm going to look for a case that is specifically lightweight. Otherwise I would use this case.Also wanted to say, I ordered the wine red/pink one, and is exactly like the picture. Which I wouldn't call wine red???? I was hoping the pic would be wrong and it would be more reddish, but nope.... It's just like the picture. Nice color, just know that it's more of a plum color rather than wine red, imo.
